{"tid":2402584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲更新對港旅遊警示：提醒中國澳洲雙重國籍的港人更改國籍","createTime":"2021-02-10T13:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T15:09:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea954cabbb49ad96069b01ea18010370cf408acf","tid":2402584,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jZ7QkdMJlhaba4puH4W2lQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ni43NjkyMzA3NjkyMzA3/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/ZxLOxbTyWddFjWU5ZHHeDA--~B/aD01NTg7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/onccinstantnews.com/744663dd333ec94725dea2e36e24e3e1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjZ7QkdMJlhaba4puH4W2lQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ni43NjkyMzA3NjkyMzA3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZxLOxbTyWddFjWU5ZHHeDA--~B%2FaD01NTg7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F744663dd333ec94725dea2e36e24e3e1&h=ff32cd6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=efdfeb7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】澳洲政府周三（10日）更新對香港的旅遊提示，指香港不再承認雙重國籍，建議擁有中國、澳洲國籍的國民若希望在香港被視為澳洲公民，要到入境處作變更國籍申請。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲政府早前已列中國內地和香港為「不要前往」，警示級別沒有變更。最新警示雙重國籍提示，提醒澳洲人隨着香港實施《中國國籍法》，香港特區不再承認雙重國籍，擁有中國與澳洲雙重國籍的人士若想被視為澳洲公民，需向入境處登記聲明變更國籍。<br />\n<br />\n警示續指，如果香港政府視相關雙重國籍人士為中國公民，即使他在入境時使用澳洲護照或其他國家護照，港府仍可拒絕相關人等獲得澳洲領事服務。雙重國籍公民未宣布放棄中國籍並繼續持有特區或中國護照，將被視為中國公民。警示提醒國民計劃進入中國內地或香港，要用澳洲護照入境。"},{"pid":"e4e9b7f5f80de5d20b0913c746d96df210aaa160","tid":2402584,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:35:07.000Z","msg":"篤航完了"},{"pid":"085576286675f2de61e1b1742191fd68142c93ff","tid":2402584,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56722c2d4ef56ce15e3c5e5afd2bfed878b5e262","tid":2402584,"uid":126317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:09:27.000Z","msg":"痰尿盅 隻賣港賊，唔該出嚟講兩句"}]}